<p><b>How can I write notes on a PDF for free?</b> Open your document in the Acrobat online PDF editor. Click the Add Comment icon and select whether you'd like the comment to be visible as text on the document or whether you want it to show up as a comment icon. Make your comment and repeat throughout the document.</p>
